FW photos from Egyptshendrinsf I have returned from Egypt We had a great time The weather was great and the tour was well organized But it is good to be back I will write more later They missed me at work it looks like I will be busy for a while Original Message From Gillian Grant mailto Sent Sunday February AM To mom GRANT Bruce S Grant lexow grant Subject photos from Egypt Dear mom Bruce and Unlce Lex Greetings from an overcast and chilly Istanbul It is Sunday afternoon and I am back safe and sound I hope Bruce your travels went well Yesterday morning I took a cab to the Islamic museum and it was indeed as good as I had hoped and empty cheap to boot No problems with our Hashem our agent picking me up and transferring me back to the hotel and then the airport I met Brandi in the waiting lounge and it seems she too had the same distressing reports about Doing Egypt on your own on the cheap She was harrassed a lot sexually and otherwise and generally felt lost and unhappy a lot I think we definitely made the right move to do it the way we did My flight was uneventful and her boyfriend met us at the airport and had gotten us a ride home I had a great homecoming My good friend Christine from Ireland came over and we went to a fun party given by a gay Brit friend last night home after pm I got up and went to church and it was nice to see friends there Afterwards coffee with my friend Terry and then shopping and relaxing here My home is fine and Sultan is happy to have me back What a super vacation I am relaxed and energized Have already done a load of laundry and soon will do yoga Great to hear from you mom from the boat and hope you have a great time Nice that you arrived to find flowers from the Millers Enjoy Bruce I suppose you could copy this letter to send on to mom I assume you got the same email I did from her on the boat I love you all gillian Do You Yahoo Get personalized email addresses from Yahoo Mail only a year Bruce I at Abu Simbeljpg Bruce I at Edfujpg Bruce i at Hippostyle halljpg

FW photos from Egyptshendrinsf Original Message From Gillian Grant mailto Sent Monday February PM To mom GRANT Bruce S Grant lexow grant Subject photos from Egypt Dear Mom uncle lex and bruce Hi from a chilly rainy Istanbul Yes I am back to the land of no sun very overcast Sunlight was so nice in Egypt I can hardly believe I was in Cairo just a few days ago Had a good day back at work I was complemented in front of my peers for my work on the web site my journal excerpt and the photos Everyone is pretty impressed Nice to get positive feedback My job doesnt provide a lot of that Have yall seen the slide show and read my journal on the through the Isik web page I sent out a mass mailing a while back with a link to it I forgot about a conference I am presenting at is this very week I am presenting with three female teacher friends two other Americans one turk I wrote a long poem for my part and tomorrow we do a run through in front of our peers at Isik Anyway I am off to Ankara hopefully on the romantic luxurious night train Wednesday evening probably express bus back for Saturday night WIsh me luck Nice to get back to my routine Picked up the Michaelangelo book again at the gym and made a big salad I love you all gillian Do You Yahoo Get personalized email addresses from Yahoo Mail only a year Bruce I at Nefertiti temple Abu Simbeljpg Bruce I at hotel pool with pyramidsjpg Edfu templejpg

More photos from Egyptshendrinsf I had a great weekend I spent most of it in bed reading The weather is still crappy here Hope you had a great weekend too pyramidsjpg hippostyle halljpg Bruce I at Nefertiti temple Abu Simbeljpg
